]], Bacolod\n*[[University of San Jose \u2013 Recoletos]], Cebu\n\n==[[Order of Friars Minor]]==\n*Our Lady of the Angels Seminary\n*San Jose Parochial School\n*St. Francis School\n*Our Lady of Montecelli Learning Center\n\n==[[Order of Friars Minor Capuchin]]==\n*[[Lourdes School of Mandaluyong]]\n*[[Lourdes School of Quezon City]]\n\n==[[Dominican Order|Order of Preachers]]==\n*[[Aquinas School]] San Juan City\n*[[Angelicum School Iloilo]]\n*[[Colegio de San Juan de Letran]], Manila\n*Dominican College, San Juan City\n*[[Dominican College of Santa Rosa|Dominican College, Santa Rosa City]]\n*[[Dominican College of Tarlac|Dominican College, Tarlac]]\n*Dominican School, Angeles City\n*Dominican School, Apalit\n*Dominican School, Calabanga\n*Dominican School, Camalig\n*Dominican School, Cebu\n*Dominican School, Dagupan City\n*Dominican School, Manila\n*Dominican School, Pilar\n*Dominican School, Santa Rita\n*San Pedro College - Davao City\n*[[Pontifical and Royal University of Santo Tomas, The Catholic University of the Philippines|University of Santo Tomas]], Manila\n*[[University of Santo Tomas - Legazpi]]\n*[[University of Santo Tomas - Sta. Rosa]] Laguna\n*University of Santo Tomas - General Santos\n*UST Angelicum College, Quezon City\n\n==[[Order of Saint Augustine]]==\n*[[Colegio San Agustin \u2013 Bacolod]]\n*[[Colegio San Agustin \u2013 Bi\u00f1an]]\n*[[Colegio San Agustin \u2013 Makati]]\n*[[University of San Agustin]], Iloilo City\n\n==[[Order of Saint Benedict]]==\n*[[Holy Family Academy (Philippines)|Holy Family Academy, Angeles]]\n*[[St. Agnes' Academy Legazpi City]]\n*[[St. Scholastica's Academy Marikina]]\n*[[St. Scholastica's Academy, San Fernando]]\n*[[St. Scholastica's College Manila]]\n*[[San Beda College Alabang]]\n*[[San Beda University|San Beda University Manila]]\n*[[San Beda University|San Beda University Integrated Basic Education Department]]\n\n====Augustinian Sisters of Our Lady of Consolation====\n*La Consolacion College - Baao\n*La Consolacion College - Bacolod\n*[[La Consolacion College \u2013 Bi\u00f1an]]\n*La Consolacion College - Caloocan\n*La Consolacion College - Iriga\n*La Consolacion College - Isabela\n*La Consolacion College - Pasig\n*[[La Consolacion College \u2013 Manila]]\n*La Consolacion College - Tanauan\n*La Consolacion College - Valenzuela\n*[[La Consolacion University Philippines]], Malolos\n\n==[[Religious of the Assumption]]==\n*[[Assumption Antipolo]]\n*[[Assumption Iloilo]]\n*Assumption Passi\n*[[Assumption College San Lorenzo | Assumption San Lorenzo]]\n*San Juan Nepomuceno School\n\n==[[Religious Sisters of Mercy]] (RSM)==\n*[[Fatima College of Camiguin]], Mambajao, Camiguin <ref>http://eskwelahan.com/camiguin/fcc.html</ref>\n\n==[[Religious of the Virgin Mary]] (RVM)== \nSee<ref>http://www.rvmonline.net/?q=education</ref>\n* [[Saint Mary's College of Quezon City]] \n* St. Mary\u2019s Academy, Hagonoy, Bulacan \n* St. Mary\u2019s Academy, Guagua, Pampanga \n*[[St. Mary's College of Meycauayan|St. Mary\u2019s College]], Meycauayan, Bulacan\n* St. Mary\u2019s Academy, Sta. Ana, Manila City\n* St. Mary\u2019s Academy, Pasay City, Metro Manila \n*[[St. Mary\u2019s Academy]], Yakal, Manila City\n*[[St. Mary\u2019s Academy]], Caloocan City\n* St. Mary\u2019s College, Boac, Marinduque \n*[[St. Mary\u2019s Academy]], Sto. Ni\u00f1o, Bulacan\n* St. Mary\u2019s College, Catbalogan City, Western Samar \n*[[St. Mary\u2019s College (Borongan)|St. Mary\u2019s College]], [[Borongan City|Borongan]], Eastern Samar \n*[[St. Mary\u2019s Academy]], Roxas City. Capiz\n*[[St. Mary\u2019s Academy]], Dipolog City, Zamboanga del Norte \n*[[St. Rita's College]], Balingasag, Misamis Oriental \n*[[St. Mary\u2019s Academy]], Talisayan, Misamis Oriental \n*[[St. Mary\u2019s Academy]], Jasaan, Misamis Oriental \n*[[Lourdes College]], Cagayan de Oro City \n*[[St. Mary\u2019s Academy]], Cagayan de Oro City \n*[[St. Michael's College (Iligan)|St. Michael\u2019s College]], Iligan City\n*[[Christ the King Colleg